        "action": "Ban homework for Year 11 students a few months before the GCSE exams",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "I think that homework should be banned because it gives us little time to revise. It takes up most of our time at home that we have after school, and leaves us with only maybe 1 hour to revise after the homework. One hour a day is not enough for GCSE students.",
